      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SEMI PEAKIN' (7) missed the frame latest (23.08) when fourth over 400m at The Gardens in a NG. Has already won two times from this draw. Looks the one to beat with even luck. GO FORWARD KENNY (5) spotted a start but wound up strongly late and finished second and beaten 2 lengths (18.41) at Richmond in Grade 5. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from four starts. Leading player again. FASCINATE GEORGE (4) showed good early burn and was there until turning but swamped late to finish 7th at The Gardens in Grade 4/5 company. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and six minor placings to his credit. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. AUSSIE RATTLER (8) placed last time and is worth some thought.",
